(264, '2014中国机器人大赛暨ROBOCUP公开赛学术论坛日程安排', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20170612/701e3a4d848c0121ff99160e00358913.jpg', 18, '', '', '', 343, 0, '', '', '', 1394637960, '<table style="color:#333333;font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size:12px;line-height:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;" class="ke-zeroborder" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td id="text" style="font-size:14px;line-height:2.2;font-family:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;padding:10px 0px;">\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　</span><strong><span style="font-size:14px;">　学术论坛日程安排</span></strong> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　10:00 – 18:10，2014-10-10，合肥</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　主持人：原魁，研究员，中国科学院自动化研究所</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　地点：安徽国际会展中心报告厅（合肥经开区金寨南路和繁华大道交口A馆）</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　10:00 – 10:20 现场嘉宾介绍，合肥市领导致辞，组委会领导致辞</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　10:20 – 10:50 特邀报告一 发展自动化与机器人的思考</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin:0px;padding:0px;">\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">　　</span> \n				</div>\n				<div style="margin: