(351, '2017中国机器人大赛比赛规则发布', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20170630/073ad2d4f4d9b6c5e3b561d78da3ca1b.jpg', 101, '', '', '', 495, 1, '', '', '', 1498813020, '<span style="box-sizing:border-box;color:#3B3B3B;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:36px;text-indent:48px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">2017中国机器人大赛比赛规则正式发布，请点击下载链接进行下载。</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:36px;text-indent:48px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">所有项目规则都已发布。</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;font-size:16px;white-space:normal;color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:36px;text-indent:48px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">请关注中国自动化学会机器人竞赛与培训部微信公众号：drct-caa 的最新通知。</span><br />\n<span style="font-size:16px;"></span><br />\n<a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20170721/20170721065333_52948.zip" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:18px;color:#003399;"><strong>规则下载（7月21日更新版）</strong></span></a><br />\n<span style="font-size:18px;color:#003399;"><strong></strong></span><br />\n<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n<div style="box-sizing:border-box;color:#3B3B3B;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;white-space:normal;text-align:right;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;">2017 中国机器人大赛组委会 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \n</div>\n<div style="box-sizing:border-box;color:#3B3B3B;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;white-space:normal;text-align:right;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;">&nbsp; 二〇一七年六月五日 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1