(505, '重要通知||关于2018中国机器人大赛白酒学院住宿预订截止时间更改的通知', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20180720/85fba8d27a44d907fe018aace7113736.jpg', 101, '', '', '', 1, 0, '', '', '', 1532072160, '<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">各参赛队：</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">&nbsp; </span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;text-indent:28px;white-space:normal;background-color:#BBE3D3;font-size:18px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">由于目前白酒学院预订人员较多，且</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">白酒学院提供酒店式服务，被品等需要提前按量采购，</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">预定截止以发送邮件时间为准，</span></span></span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;text-indent:28px;white-space:normal;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">若超过预定截止时间将不再接受预定，也不接受现场预定。</span></strong><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 为更好地给参赛队提供住宿服务，对2018中国机器人大赛白酒学院住宿预订截止时间作如下修改：</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;text-align:center;">\n	<strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF2941;">预订截止时间更改为：2018年7月25日</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 请有需要的参赛队及时<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-indent:36px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">按照相关要求与宜宾负责白酒学院住宿预订工作人员联系并</span>预订，点击下方蓝色字体下载相关预订回执。</span> \n</p>\n<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="font-size:18px;"></span><a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180720/20180720074644_44020.docx" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:18px;">住宿回执单</span></a>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#FF2941;">&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">说明：</span></strong></span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 1.由于宿舍为瓷砖， 考虑到安全问题，故不提供一次性拖鞋，由组委会提供塑料拖鞋，无须自带。</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 2.<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">场馆附近酒店较少，市内酒店基本均在长江对面，故从市内大部分酒店至场馆需经长江大桥，大桥早高峰堵车较为严重，为避免耽误比赛，建议各参赛队</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">预订大赛推荐白酒学院宿舍，白酒学院距离场馆3.5km，且在比赛期间组委会安排班车接送。如有提前预定其他酒店且尚</span><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">未付款，建议退订酒店，尽早预定大赛推荐宿舍！</span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:medium;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-align:right;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;">中国自动化学会&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;text-align:right;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;">二〇一八年七月二十日</span> \n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(503, '重要通知||关于2018中国机器人大赛白酒学院住宿预订、成都中转大巴包车预订的通知', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20180718/dd9f39797f86c7898e6b6cd5a08ba481.jpg', 101, '', '', '', 1, 0, '', '', '', 1531910400, '<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">各参赛队：</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.目前白酒学院宿舍预订的工作正在进行，且预订人数较多，预定截止时间可能将会提前，如有需要预订白酒学院宿舍的参赛队伍，请抓紧时间按照相关要求与宜宾负责白酒学院住宿预订工作人员联系，按照相关要求进行预订，防止出现超过截止时间预订失败情况。</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.由于宜宾地处蜀南，交通不便，大赛组委会联系到成都客运站进行火车站包车接站，接站地点为：成都站，成都东站。因双流机场有大巴可直达宜宾，故不设接站。</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;鉴于本次大赛参赛人员较多，客运站需要提前进行人数统计，以便排车，如有预订需求的参赛队请及时按照相关要求发送相关信息至指定邮箱，如超过截止时间，客运站将不再提供包车服务。包车前往宜宾详情如下：</span> \n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;" />\n</span> \n</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:18px;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;">费用：136元/人，包车定点接站费用会高于客运站定价，客运站包车费用160元/人，参赛人员每人支付136元，组委会向客运站补齐剩余24元/人的差价。</span> \n	</li>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:18px;color:#666666;">预定截止日期：</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#666666;">2018年7月28日</span><span style="color:#666666;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">。请务必在截止日期前将附件（车辆预定表单）（点击本文下方蓝色字体进行下载）及缴费凭证发送至：</span><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#666666;">CRC201808S@163.com</span><span style="color:#333333;">，</span></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;">同时抄送</span><span style="color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">至weiting@caa.org.cn</span> \n	</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;display:inline !important;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div style="text-align:center;">\n	<a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180718/20180718104835_79229.doc" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:18px;"></span></a><a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180718/20180718115336_84603.doc" target="_blank"><span style="font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;font-size:18px;">车辆预定表单</span></a> \n</div>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span style="font-size:18px;color:#666666;">缴费方式：线上对公转账</span> \n	</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n	<span style="color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;text-align:justify;margin:0px;padding:0px;fon