(506, '重要通知||关于2018中国机器人大赛白酒学院住宿预订截止时间更改的通知', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20180720/bed215455fe2eab5bb206f7b58c7c399.jpg', 18, '', '', '', 1, 0, '', '', '', 1532072520, '<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">各参赛队：</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;background-color:#FFFFFF;">由于目前白酒学院预订人员较多，且</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;background-color:#FFFFFF;">白酒学院提供酒店式服务，被品等需要提前按量采购，</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">预定截止以发送邮件时间为准，</span></span></span><strong style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">若超过预定截止时间将不再接受预定，也不接受现场预定。</span></strong><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 为更好地给参赛队提供住宿服务，对2018中国机器人大赛白酒学院住宿预订截止时间作如下修改：</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;text-align:center;">\n	<strong style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF2941;">预订截止时间更改为：2018年7月25日</span></strong> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 请有需要的参赛队及时<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-indent:36px;">按照相关要求与宜宾负责白酒学院住宿预订工作人员联系并</span>预订，点击下方蓝色字体下载相关预订回执。<br />\n	<div style="text-align:center;">\n		<span style="text-indent:2em;"><a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180720/20180720074555_99036.docx" target="_blank">住宿回执单</a></span><span style="text-indent:2em;"></span>\n	</div>\n</span>\n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#FF2941;">&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">说明：</span></strong></span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 1.由于宿舍为瓷砖， 考虑到安全问题，故不提供一次性拖鞋，由组委会提供塑料拖鞋，无须自带。</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; 2.<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;background-color:#FFFFFF;">场馆附近酒店较少，市内酒店基本均在长江对面，故从市内大部分酒店至场馆需经长江大桥，大桥早高峰堵车较为严重，为避免耽误比赛，建议各参赛队</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">预订大赛推荐白酒学院宿舍，白酒学院距离场馆3.5km，且在比赛期间组委会安排班车接送。如有提前预定其他酒店且尚</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;background-color:#FFFFFF;">未付款，建议退订酒店，尽早预定大赛推荐宿舍！</span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:medium;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;text-indent:2em;">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;text-align:justify;font-size:14px;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-size:14px;text-align:right;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;">中国自动化学会&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-size:14px;text-align:right;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;">二〇一八年七月二十日</span> \n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL),
