(509, '关于2018中国机器人大赛成都中转大巴包车预定、住宿预定延期的通知', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20180802/d8432b2229ef6ee179d4d331c0d2d6c2.jpg', 101, '', '', '', 1, 0, '', '', '', 1533203220, '<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">各位老师、同学：</span>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;根据宜宾白酒学院酒店预订反馈，近期有大量队伍发现自己预定酒店交通不便，在白酒学院住宿预订截止后申请预订<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">大赛推荐</span><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">白酒学院</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">住宿</span><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">。为满足此部分参赛师生需求，组委会临时决定，将开放</span></span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">今天、明天两天</span></strong><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">白酒学院住宿申请，请大家务必在</span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">8月3日24时前</span></strong><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">按照相关要求发送邮件预定，预定流程及联系方式不变。8月3日24时之后的申请不论何种原因均不再予以预订。</span><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;" />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;">\n	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;同时，关于成都中转包车预定也将开放</span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">今天、明天两天</span></strong><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#000000;"><span style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">，如有预订需求，</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;background-color:#FFFFFF;">请务必在</span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;font-size:14px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">8月3日24时前</span></strong><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;background-color:#FFFFFF;">按照相关要求发送邮件预定包车服务。</span></span></span></span>\n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(510, '关于2018中国机器人大赛成都中转大巴包车预定、住宿预定延期的通知', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20180802/34e686b16ffa9f95e80af47604afadf7.jpg', 18, '', '', '', 1, 0, '', '', '', 1533203400, '<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">各位老师、同学：</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;根据宜宾白酒学院酒店预订反馈，近期有大量队伍发现自己预定酒店交通不便，在白酒学院住宿预订截止后申请预订<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;">大赛推荐</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;">白酒学院</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;">住宿</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;">。为满足此部分参赛师生需求，组委会临时决定，将开放</span></span><strong style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;">今天、明天两天</span></strong><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;">白酒学院住宿申请，请大家务必在</span><strong style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;">8月3日24时前</span></strong><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;">按照相关要求发送邮件预定，预定流程及联系方式不变。8月3日24时之后的申请不论何种原因均不再予以预订。</span><br style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;" />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style="box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;padding:0px;clear:both;color:#555555;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;">\n	<span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;同时，关于成都中转包车预定也将开放</span><strong style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">今天、明天两天</span></strong><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#000000;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;">，如有预订需求，</span><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;">请务必在</span><strong style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;font-size:14px;background-color:#BBE3D3;"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:18px;color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF;">8月3日24时前</span></strong><span style="box-sizing:border-box;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#555555;">按照相关要求发送邮件预定包车服务。</span></span></span></span> \n</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL),
