(44, '报名须知', 20, 'about', 'about', 1, NULL, 10, 0, 1, '', '', '', 0, NULL, '<div style="text-align:center;">\n	<div style="white-space:normal;text-align:center;">\n		<span style="font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;"><strong>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:19.2000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			<b>2018年中国机器人大赛报名须知</b><b><o:p></o:p></b>\n		</p>\n<br />\n</strong></span> \n	</div>\n<span style="white-space:normal;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;"> \n	<div style="text-align:left;">\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="white-space:normal;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:#FFFFFF;">\n			一、总则\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			1.&nbsp;<span>所有参加</span>2018中国机器人大赛的指导老师、参赛队员，都必须在报名系统中进行注册；\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			2.&nbsp;填报报名信息前请仔细阅读本须知，提交的各项报名资料必须真实有效。提交虚假信息的行为会受到中国自动化学会各项机器人竞赛活动禁赛的处罚；\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			3.&nbsp;<span>关于报名过程中的任何疑问，请通过邮件进行询问和沟通，邮件地址：</span>liujie@caa.org.cn。邮件主题中请注明“报名咨询”。\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:#FFFFFF;">\n			&nbsp;\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:#FFFFFF;">\n			二、报名流程\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			1.&nbsp;<span>报名起止日期为</span>2018年6月1日至6月20日。请在此期间及时提交报名信息，并确保其真实、有效。（报名截止后，报名信息将无法修改）\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			2.&nbsp;报名审核工作概述：\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:42.1000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			l&nbsp;一级审核由赛事负责人或指定人员完成，主要审核照片及填报信息的完整性、有效性，不做参赛资格审查。\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:42.1000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			l&nbsp;二级审核由赛项负责人完成，主要审核参赛队的参赛资格。\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			3.&nbsp;请按下列要求缴纳注册费。\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21.1000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			【缴费方式】银行转账/支付宝\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21.1000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			【账户名称】中国自动化学会\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21.1000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			<span>【开</span> <span>户</span> <span>行】中国农业银行北京科院南路支行</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21.1000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			<span>【账</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>号】</span>11250101040011739\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21.1000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			【<span>支</span> <span>付</span> <span>宝</span>】caa_alipay@126.com\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			4.&nbsp;<span>完成缴费的参赛队，请及时在报名系统中上传</span>“银行转账凭证”的扫描件，上传的图片文件<span>格式为</span>jpg，图文清晰、完整。请不要涂改、修改缴费凭证上的任何信息。\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21.1000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			&nbsp;\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:#FFFFFF;">\n			三、报名注意事项\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			1.&nbsp;<span>请用</span>Chrome浏览器登录报名系统，请不要在同一台电脑上同时登录不同的账户；\n		</p>\n	</div>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div style="text-align:center;">\n	<span style="white-space:normal;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;">\n	<div style="text-align:left;">\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			2.&nbsp;请报名人员认真填写参赛人员信息（含参赛队名称、人员姓名、类别、身份证号码、联系方式、发票相关信息等），并确保其真实性、准确性；\n		</p>\n	</div>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div style="text-align:center;">\n	<span style="white-space:normal;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;">\n	<div style="text-align:left;">\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			3.&nbsp;请确认所有参赛人员的排列顺序。相关信息会在参赛证件、参赛证明、获奖证书等重要比赛文件中体现。\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			4.&nbsp;由于参赛队信息填报原因产生的任何错误，在相关文件完成制作后一律不予修改；\n		</p>\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			5.&nbsp;<span>报名时必须上传本人近期</span>2寸证件照，照片要求如下：\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:24.2000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			JPG格式、头像端正、五官清晰、大小不超过500K、背景颜色为白色、浅蓝色或灰色。该照片将用于赛事建档及相关证件制作，请慎重提交。\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:24.2000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			参考照片请见下图（图片来源于网络，仅供参考）：\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<br />\n		</p>\n		<blockquote style="white-space:normal;margin:0px 0px 0px 40px;border:none;padding:0px;">\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>\n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n		</blockquote>\n		<p class="MsoNormal" style="white-space:normal;background:white;">\n			<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n		</p>\n		<div>\n			<br />\n		</div>\n		<blockquote style="white-space:normal;margin:0px 0px 0px 40px;border:none;padding:0px;">\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="background:white;">\n				<span style="font-size:16px;"></span> \n			</p>\n			<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:center;background:white;">\n				<img src="/static/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20170701/20170701030201_64377.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/static/kindeditor/php/../attached/image/20170701/20170701030201_95015.jpg" alt="" />\n			</p>\n		</blockquote>\n<span style="background-color:white;">\n		<p class="16" style="margin-left:21.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;background:#FFFFFF;">\n			6.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>注册费减免政策：参加过</span>2018RoboCup机器人世界杯中国赛的参赛人员可获得注册费减免资格。请有减免资格的参赛队伍指导教师将附件一“费用减免回执表”统计好后，发送至<a href="mailto:liujie@caa.org.cn">liujie@caa.org.cn</a><span>（邮件标题请注明</span>“申请注册费减免”）。审核通过的参赛人员可减免一半的参赛费用，并在收到邮件确认通知后，进行付费操作。\n		</p>\n		<p class="MsoNormal">\n			<span>7.&nbsp; &nbsp; 各参赛队在报名截止前务必填写附件二</span>“2018中国机器人大赛安全须知”、附件三“2018中国机器人大赛授权许可”， 并将签字盖章后的扫描件或照片上传至报名系统。\n		</p>\n</span><br />\n		<div>\n			<br />\n		</div>\n<a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180531/20180531122835_12909.pdf" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:16px;">下载：2018中国机器人大赛报名须知</span></a><br style="white-space:normal;" />\n<a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180531/20180531122911_43433.docx" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:16px;">附件一：2018中国机器人大赛费用减免申请表</span></a><br />\n<span style="font-size:16px;"></span><a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180531/20180531123004_41878.pdf" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:16px;">附件二：2018中国机器人大赛安全须知</span></a><br />\n<span style="font-size:16px;"></span><a class="ke-insertfile" href="/static/kindeditor/attached/file/20180531/20180531123029_84889.pdf" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:16px;">附件三：2018中国机器人大赛授权许可</span></a><br />\n	</div>\n</span> \n	<div style="text-align:left;">\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n	<strong style="white-space:normal;"><br />\n</strong> \n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20170630/9026bb55659340182541cf9d4f15cd1c.jpg', 'static/kindeditor/attached/image/20170630/a5367387c4ae45d71bbba107ea6788b4.jpg', NULL, NULL),
